 Salon Riyora – Beauty Salon Booking Web Application

Project Overview
Salon Riyora is an interactive beauty salon booking web application that allows users to explore salon services and book appointments online. The website is designed with a responsive layout and user-friendly interface.

Features
- Display salon services using card layouts
- Online appointment booking form
- JavaScript form validation
- Image slider on the home page
- Booking confirmation popup
- Smooth navigation and UI effects

Website Pages
- **Home Page** – Introduction, image slider, featured services  
- **Services Page** – List of salon services with images  
- **Booking Page** – Appointment booking form  
- **Contact Page** – Contact details and contact form  

Technologies Used
- HTML  
- CSS  
- Bootstrap  
- JavaScript  

Purpose
This project demonstrates the development of a responsive and interactive salon booking website using front-end web technologies.
